name: AddictiveFuture_Realistic_SemiAsian
description:
⚡️ Intro

This model is mainly intended to create nice looking semi-asian girls (SFW&NSFW).
Of course, you can try generating other things besides women 😎 Feel free to share Your work 💪

Inspired by QGO - PromptingReal. I love quality of nude pictures from that model 💙
So I merged it with GirlMix and RealDosMix using sd-webui-supermerger to get semi-asian results.
I also tried to merge it with models RV, AM, SLDR, ICBINP, Am I Real, epiCRealism, rMadArt, 3moon REAL_Photo. But I didn't get satisfying results. It was hard to get good private parts of the body 🙄
So... click ⬇️ Show More ⬇️ link below, have fun... and try not to spend all your money for renting GPU's 😄😄😄

⚙️ Recommended Settings

For girls and 30-40 years old women
CFG Scale around 5
Clip Skip 2-3

For 50-60 years old and elderly women
CFG Scale 5-10
Clip Skip 1

Sampler DPM++ 2M SDE Karras // alternatively DPM++ 2S a Karras or DPM++ 2M Karras
Sampling Steps around 30 for tests, 60+ for final work
VAE vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

You just need to do experiments and find your sweet spot. Check my XY plots for inspiration.

✍️ Recommended workflow

  • Set picture size to 540x960 (for portraits) or 960x540 (for landscapes). Don't go above 1024px!

  • Put nationality into positive prompt, for example (Irish girl:1.3) or (Malaysian woman:1.3) to modify face shape and skin tone.

  • Use negative embeddings (must have!). Just use popular ones.

  • Use Lora's for better image quality

  • Do not use Celebrity / face morphing Textual Inversions because in most cases it will make your skin unnatural, pale. Better find good Lora and use it instead.

    (optional) Put age into positive prompt. Be specific. Use keywords like: XX years old, girl, woman, old lady, elderly woman.
    Combining these words will give you the best results. Examples:
    photography of German girl, 20 years old

    photography of Italian woman, 40 years old
    photography of Spanish woman, very old lady, elderly woman

✨ Recommended Lora's

  • Sharpness Tweaker

  • epi_noiseoffset

  • Photoblend (play carefully with this - shadows and brightness may kill your work)

  • LowRA (use it for professional studio photos, for non-studio use about 0.2-0.3)

  • Shiny oiled skin (use Only for nudes, otherwise it can make your faces ugly)

🧾 Recommended Embeddings (Textual Inversions)

  • NSFW Embedding (awesome TI to keep girls naked or clothed)

🌏 Nationalities (ethnicity)

I started playing with nationalities after finding this Reddit post.
Some nationalities produce sexy face outputs. You need to find your favourites.
For tests you can use sd-dynamic-prompts and this prompt.

👎 Known weak points of this model

  • Teeth 🦷 it's better to have mouth closed for non close-up photos

  • Fingers 🖖 better hide them behind (common issue in many models)

  • Imperfect nipples from the side 😭 (common issue in many models)

  • Impossiblle to generate realistic skin and body of nude grandmas 😦

🌫Outro

I hope this model will be beneficial to someone among you. If you enjoyed playing with this model, please leave a review and like other users' photos. Best regards 🖐

// all models and images were creted on Vast.ai servers (using 1x GTX4090)
// all my images were generted without inpaiting and without controlnet
// pruned versions created with stable-diffusion-webui-model-toolkit
// if you have problems with my English - contact with my secretary 🧻
